    38→ * Renders a 3D marker in VR space that can be interacted with.
    39→ * Provides visual feedback through hover states and pulsing animations.
    40→ *
    41→ * Features:
    42→ * - Clickable/tappable 3D sphere marker
    43→ * - Hover state with visual feedback
    44→ * - Pulsing animation to draw attention
    45→ * - Optional label that appears on hover
    46→ * - Customizable color and scale
    47→ *
    48→ * @example
    49→ * ```tsx
    50→ * <BaseHotspot
    51→ *   id="hotspot-1"
    52→ *   position={{ x: 0, y: 1.6, z: -2 }}
    53→ *   color="#4f46e5"
    54→ *   label="Click me"
    55→ *   onClick={() => console.log('Clicked!')}
    56→ * />
    57→ * ```
